                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab>Notitia facio ego <persName key="#Bishops" ref="#people/343"
                            >Peredeus</persName> in Dei nomine <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs>,
                        qualiter devisionem feci in <placeName
                            key="#Salae #Demesnes #Casalini/fundamenta #Petiae #Landed_possessions #Cereals #Wine #Fruits/vegetables"
                            >Rasiniano</placeName> cum <persName ref="#people/702"
                            >Sunderad</persName> nepote meo de <rs key="#Landed_possessions"
                            >res</rs> illa quas antea ividem non devisimus; in primis, de <rs
                            key="#Petiae #Cereals">campo</rs> ad Fine <rs key="#Demesnes"
                            >sundriale</rs>, una <rs key="#Petiae">petia longa</rs>, tenet capite
                        uno in Fine et latere uno tenet in alia petia longa in ipso campo, fini
                        signa posite; et alia <rs key="#Petiae">petia</rs> minore de ipso campo,
                        latere uno tenet in <rs key="#Petiae">terra</rs>
                        <persName key="#Confinia #Petiae #Priests"><name ref="Lamiteus"
                                >Lamitei</name></persName>
                        <rs>presbiteri</rs> et capite uno tenet in <rs key="#Petiae">terra</rs> de
                            <rs key="#Slave_labour">homenis</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Petiae #Slave_labour" ref="#juridical_persons/235">Sancti
                            Michaeli</orgName>, fini signa posite: quod est, inter perdictas ambas
                        petias, medietate de ipso <rs key="#Landed_possessions #Cereals">campo
                            nostro sundriale</rs>; et medietate de <rs key="#Acorns">silva</rs>
                        nostra ad <placeName key="#Size #Acorns">Capitito</placeName> maiure, latere
                        tenente in <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terra</rs>
                        <persName key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions"><name ref="Pertifunsus"
                                >Pertifuns</name></persName>, fini signa posite; excepto <rs>tres
                            modiorum et sistariorum septe</rs> de ipsa silva, qui stancliata est ad
                        parte mea ab ipso Sunderado, fini signa posite; et de <rs
                            key="#Demesnes #Wine">vinea sundriale</rs> de <rs key="#Petiae"
                            >petia</rs> maiure medietate, latere tenente da trasmontante, fini signa
                        posite; similiter de <rs key="#Demesnes #Wine">vinea sundriale</rs> de <rs
                            key="#Petiae">petia</rs> minore medietate, latere tenente da
                        trasmontante, fini signa posite: quod est inter predictas ambas petias de
                        vinea sundriale, infra ipsa clausura medietate; et de <rs
                            key="#Demesnes #Casalini/fundamenta">fundamento nostro sundriale</rs>,
                        ubi <rs key="#Salae">sala</rs> antiqua posita fuit, medietate, latere
                        tenente da transmontante, fini signa posite, sicut ex antiquo ipse
                        fundamento fuit; similiter et de <rs key="#Demesnes #Fruits/vegetables">orto
                            sundriale</rs>, quem habuet <persName
                            key="#Demesnes #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Fruits/vegetables"><name
                                ref="Pertulus">Pertulo</name></persName> ante <rs
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">casa</rs> sua medietate, latere tenente
                        da transmontante, fine signa posite. Facta notitia temporibus domno nostro
                        Desiderii et Adelchis regibus, in anno regni eorum sexto et tertio, sexto
                        calendas iunias, per indictione XV. Ex dictato viri beatissimi Peredei in
                        Dei nomine episcopi scribsi ego <persName key="#Writer #Deacons"><name
                                ref="Osprandus">Osprandus</name></persName>
                        <rs>diaconus</rs>. + Ego Peredeus exiguus episcopus in hanc breve
                        subscripsi. + Ego Sunderadu in hanc breve subscripsi. Signum + manus
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Ermicaidus"
                            >Ermicaidi</name></persName> filio quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Baruncius">Barunci</name></persName> testis. Signum + manus
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Teudebertus"
                            >Teutpert</name></persName> filio vone memorie <persName><name
                                ref="Teudeperti">Teudeperti</name></persName> testis. Signum + manus
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Willibertus"
                            >Wilipert</name></persName> filio bone memorie <persName><name
                                ref="Gisbertus">Ghispert</name></persName> testis.</ab>
                        </div>
